Accident on Lagos-Ibadan Expressway leaves many dead,injured.


Many people have been feared dead in an accident at Fidiwo, Ogun state, along Lagos-Ibadan Expressway.


According toÂ Punch , the incident happened around 9 am on Tuesday, January 18, when a fully loaded commercial bus heading for Lagos rammed into a diesel tanker.


The tanker had been reportedly stopped by men of the Federal Road Safety Corps, Oyo State Command, when the accident happened.












